name: The God
description:
Indonesia is an archipelago country, which located in the ring of fire and that fact makes Indonesia has many mountains. Several of those mountains are active mountains that can be erupted at certain times. Almost all mountains have a folklore story behind them, however most of them are similar. That is about the dragon as the God who protect the mountain itself.

This work is part of a charity to help victims of the natural disaster from Mount Semeru eruption, every sale in the first market will be 100% donated to the victims, through sewon NFT #tezos4semeru
